/div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y35 ffd fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">指出一切万法为大空，而不是单空，相当于禅宗的顿门派，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y41 ffd fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">直指心的本来面目。<span class="_ _8"></span>对利根者来说，<span class="_ _8"></span>因为根基与善根已经成</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y42 ffd fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">熟，<span class="_ _8"></span>故与中观应成派的教理十分相应，<span class="_ _8"></span>一下子就能契入这种</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y43 ffd fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">境界。 </div><div class="t m0 x23 h4 y39 ffd fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">而中观自续派，<span class="_ _8"></span>是先将一切万法抉择为名言中存在、<span class="_ _8"></span>胜</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y3a ffd fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">义中是单空，<span class="_ _8"></span>然后再进一步将层次提高，<span class="_ _8"></span>慢慢趋入离四边八</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y3b ffd fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">戏的大空性，<span class="_ _8"></span>与中观应成派的观点汇为一体。<span class="_ _8"></span>这相当于禅宗</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y3c ffd fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">的渐门派。 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
